WEBVTT

00:00:00.049 --> 00:00:02.326
Food is design.

00:00:02.350 --> 00:00:04.892
It is design when you compose plates,

00:00:04.916 --> 00:00:09.433
but it is amazing, even better
and most delightful design

00:00:09.457 --> 00:00:10.754
when it's about the units.

00:00:10.778 --> 00:00:11.955
[Small thing.]

00:00:11.979 --> 00:00:13.182
[Big idea.]

00:00:16.714 --> 00:00:18.290
"Pasta" comes from Latin,

00:00:18.314 --> 00:00:20.180
and it means "paste."

00:00:20.204 --> 00:00:24.130
It's about putting together
water and some powder,

00:00:24.154 --> 00:00:26.660
so that you can actually shape it.

00:00:26.684 --> 00:00:29.700
There are cultures in the world
that use rice powder,

00:00:29.724 --> 00:00:32.131
others use soy powder.